title: Damir Mehmedovic
text:
Damir Mehmedovic (born 11 December 1997) is an Austrian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="1.%20FC%20Lokomotive%20Leipzig">1. FC Lokomotive Leipzig</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Austrian%20Football%20First%20League">Austrian Football First League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Blau-Wei%C3%9F%20Linz">FC Blau-Weiß Linz</a> on 5 August 2016 in a game against <a href="SC%20Wiener%20Neustadt">SC Wiener Neustadt</a>.
